\s Ukuvalelisa kukaJesu
\p
\v 16 Okwesikhatshana futhi kaliyikungibona\x + 12.35.\x*, kubuye kube yisikhatshana libe selingibona\x + 14.19.\x*, ngoba mina ngiya kuBaba\x + 16.10,28. 14.12.\x*.
\v 17 Ngakho \add abanye\add* kubafundi bakhe bakhulumisana \add besithi\add*: Kuyini lokho akutsho kithi: Okwesikhatshana, futhi kaliyikungibona, kubuye kube yisikhatshana libe selingibona; lokuthi: Ngoba mina ngiya kuBaba\x + 16.16.\x*?
\v 18 Basebesithi: Kuyini lokhu akutshoyo \add ukuthi\add*: Okwesikhatshana? Kasazi ukuthi utshoni.
\p
\v 19 UJesu wayesesazi ukuthi babethanda ukumbuza\x + Mat. 9.4.\x*, wasesithi kubo: Liyabuzana ngalokho yini, ukuthi ngithe: Okwesikhatshana futhi kaliyikungibona, kubuye kube yisikhatshana libe selingibona\x + 16.16.\x*?
\v 20 Ngiqinisile, ngiqinisile, ngithi kini: Lina lizakhala lilile\x + Mark. 16.10.\x*, kodwa umhlaba uzathokoza; futhi lizakuba losizi lina, kodwa usizi lwenu luzaphendulwa lube yintokozo\x + Mat. 5.4.\x*.
\v 21 Owesifazana nxa ebeletha ulobuhlungu, ngoba ihola lakhe selifikile; kodwa nxa esebelethe usane, kasakhumbuli ubuhlungu, ngenxa yentokozo yokuthi kuzelwe umuntu emhlabeni\x + Isa. 26.17. Isa. 13.8. Jer. 6.24. Mark. 13.8.\x*.
\v 22 Ngakho lani-ke lilosizi khathesi\x + 16.6.\x*; kodwa ngizabuya ngilibone, lenhliziyo yenu ithokoze, njalo kakho ongalemuka intokozo yenu\x + Hlab. 33.21. Luka 24.41,52. Joha. 20.20. Seb. 2.46. 13.52. Seb. 8.8. 1 Pet. 1.8.\x*.
