\v 23 Langalolosuku kaliyikungibuza lutho\x + 14.20. 16.26.\x*. Ngiqinisile, ngiqinisile, ngithi kini: Loba kuyini elizakucela kuBaba ebizweni lami uzalinika\x + 14.13. Mat. 7.7.\x*.
